## VS Code workspace extensions

### moalamri.inline-fold — Log line folding ⚠️ DEPRECATED

> **Extension marked as deprecated** as of 2026. Still functional but no longer maintained.
> Alternatives identified if a migration becomes necessary:
> - `ilverism.inline-tag-context-hider-vsc` — same inline-fold concept, regex-based
> - `ldlework.matched-line-dimmer` — dims full lines matching a regex (tag: "log dimmer")

- Install: Extensions panel → search "Inline Fold" by Mohamad Al Amri, or `ext install moalamri.inline-fold`
- Config: `.vscode/settings.json` (already committed in this repo)
- Effect: all `hw_log_*`, `sys_log_*`, `input_log_*`, `combus_log_*`, `log_err/warn/info/dbg`
  calls are folded to a `⊟ log` marker in C/C++ files.
- Click the marker or select the line to unfold temporarily.
- `"unfoldedOpacity": 0.7` keeps unfolded log lines visually dimmed vs logic code.
- To disable temporarily: comment out `"inlineFold.regex"` in settings.json.


